{"tid":657572,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【跟 Huawei 風？】三鏡頭 iPhone X 曝光！","createTime":"2018-05-08T08:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T14:10:44.000Z","uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"195f7e64662afe8c97062bedf05d4bbf9f296abc","tid":657572,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"Huawei 今年推出的 P20 Pro，其 Leica 三鏡頭主相機的拍攝質素極高，受到不少追棒。所謂「橋唔怕舊最緊要受」，Apple 亦有傳會在新的 iPhone 中，加入三鏡頭主相機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，有台灣科技產業分析師蒲得宇在一分報告指出，2019 年下半年度推出的 iPhone，至少會有一款配備三鏡頭主相機，但分析師就沒有透露有關三鏡頭主相機的任何細節。<br />\n<br />\n去年 iPhone X 推出時，曾經有分析指其 TrueDepth 前相機鏡頭系統，其他廠商要用一年至一年半時間，技術才能追上，看來今次 Apple 亦會用一年多時間，才能追近 Huawei 的三鏡頭拍攝技術。"},{"pid":"c86749ff50e165bb0a871a1710d5d0986ac0bc00","tid":657572,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"又有屎爲飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4360b6dea48ace3fb8d4e04d2d133c507c9ad24","tid":657572,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">華為或成最大贏國</span></span>"},{"pid":"382fb4fde09d76785b40cd099fd846a52772fcec","tid":657572,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">華為或成最大贏家</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5f7f8149079e83455b4203ad37f971386cfaa479","tid":657572,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdd47e0487a1005dc2f34bdafc45f3ebcbd8b3f8","tid":657572,"uid":73731,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"apple永遠係原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次huawei又踏時光機抄apple<br />\n<br />\n唔準話我係idog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif